data.description: Historic and Grand Home on large 66 hundredths of an acre lot (28,750 square feet), flat and cleared with plenty of room for ample parking.  Features original woodwork,  leaded and beveled glass windows.   Tons of old-world charm.  Located in the center and heart of Commercial activity by Safeway, medical offices and I-5. This large, elegant old home is now zoned c-1 commercial, can continue to be used as residential housing or as a commercial business.  City verified it can be re-zoned to Multi-family R:20 and could have up to 13 residential units on the property.  City also verified it is sub-dividable. (Buyers to verify all with Centralia City Planning).  Don't miss this great opportunity.
